"{\n  \"correct\": \"no\",\n  \"explanation\": \"The code incorrectly uses the seaborn library by calling the lmplot function inside the map function of FacetGrid. The lmplot function is a figure-level function and should not be used inside the map function of FacetGrid.\",\n  \"patch\": \"5c5,6\\n< g = sns.FacetGrid(data=tips, col='time', row='sex')\\n< g.map(sns.lmplot, 'total_bill', 'tip')\\n---\\n> g = sns.FacetGrid(data=tips, col='time', row='sex')\\n> g.map(sns.regplot, 'total_bill', 'tip')\\n\"\n}"